c supports baby\'s developing immune system*. Made with Zinc for immune support* and organic agave, a natural nectar that is safe for infants and toddlers 6 months and up. Give 2 ml for babies age 6-11 months and 3 ml for babies and toddlers 1-3 years for year-round immune support*. The measured syringe makes dosing easy and accurate.Yummy Natural Grape FlavorYour little one will love the delicious natural grape flavor. You can feel good that Zarbees Baby Immune Support syrup is made from carefully selected ingredients inspired by nature and backed by science. Our kids immune support is free of drugs, alcohol, artificial sweeteners, high fructose corn syrup, & gluten. From Zarbee’s, founded by pediatrician and father, Dr. Zak Zarbock, and the #1 Pediatrician Recommended Immune Support Brand for Children.*These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.'),(6, 17, 180, 'https://shopping-project.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/images/52.jpeg', 'One A Day Women\'s Gummy Multivitamin, Multivitamins for Women, 80 Ct', 'One A Day', 10.48, 300, 'Canada', '80 Ct', 'Support your health with One A Day Women\'s VitaCraves multivitamin supplement with Folic Acid, Vitamins B6 and B12 to support heart health'),(6, 17, 181, 'https://shopping-project.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/images/53.jpeg', 'Spring Valley Vitamin D3 Softgels, 5000 IU, 100 Count', 'Spring Valley', 6.24, 350, 'U.S.', '5000 IU, 100 Count', 'Welcome the Vitamin D you need every day with the Spring Valley Vitamin D3 5,000 IU Softgels Vitamin Supplement. D3 is a potent and active form of Vitamin D, which is essential for calcium absorption, bone health, immune health and healthy teeth.* The human body can produce Vitamin D3 naturally, when the skin is directly exposed to sunlight. Even though the sun can be a great source of the D3 Vitamin, for various reasons, it may be difficult for people to get an adequate amount from the sun alone. Spring Valley Vitamin D3 softgels are an easy and reliable way to help fulfill your daily needs.* These Vitamin D supplements are gluten free, dairy free and non-GMO. Spring Valley D3 Vitamins contain no artificial colors or flavors.'),(6, 17, 182, 'https://shopping-project.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/images/54.jpeg', 'Spring Valley Vitamin C with Rose Hips Supplement, 500 mg, 100 Tablets', 'Spring Valley', 5.12, 400, 'U.S.', '500 mg, 100 Tablets', 'Vitamin C is a potent antioxidant and an essential nutrient that supports immune, cardiovascular, and bone health.'),(6, 18, 183, 'https://shopping-project.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/images/55.jpeg', 'Aveeno Skin Relief Moisturizing Body Wash, Soap Free for Sensitive Skin, Fragrance Free Shower Gel, 33 oz', 'Aveeno', 13.48, 740, 'Canada', '33 oz', 'Gently cleanse while leaving itchy, dry skin feeling moisturized with Aveeno Skin Relief Fragrance-Free Body Wash. This sulfate free body wash is made with a soothing Triple Oat formula and formulated for sensitive skin. Aveeno Skin Relief Body Wash gently, but effectively cleanses while leaving itchy, dry skin feeling soothed and feeling moisturized. 91% of users agreed the skin relief body wash gently cleansed their skin without drying it out. From the dermatologist-recommended brand for over 70 years, this body wash is allergy-tested, free of fragrances, sulfates, parabens, dyes, and soaps, and is suitable for daily use. To use, squeeze body wash onto a wet pouf, washcloth, or hands. Work into a rich, creamy lather, then rinse. Use the creamy body wash as a rich shave gel for silky, smooth legs. Follow with Aveeno Skin Relief Moisturizing Lotion to lock in moisture for 24 hours as a part of your daily skincare routine.'),(6, 18, 184, 'https://shopping-project.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/images/55-1.jpeg', 'Suave Essentials Gentle Body Wash, Sweet Vanilla, 18 oz', 'Suave', 3.12, 450, 'Canada', '18 oz', 'Allow us to reintroduce ourselves! Suave Essentials Body Washes are now new and improved! New look, new sizes, and even more benefits. Fresh, Floral, Fruit, Sweet, oh my! With our new fragrance families, finding your go-to scent is as easy as pie. Your new guilty pleasure is here with the Sweet Vanilla Silk Body Wash. Invoke a rich, sensual experience with sweet notes of vanilla cream, bright sparkling rose, and nourishing jojoba oil of our gentle body soap. The delightful, long-lasting blend of oil essence will leave your skin feeling instantly hydrated and silky smooth throughout the day. Now rich with 10X the moisturizers than before, and infused with Vitamin E and vanilla extracts, you\'ll pamper your skin with every use. Gentle and perfect for everyday cleansing, our Body Wash contains absolutely no parabens or phthalates in its formulation.'),(6, 18, 185, 'https://shopping-project.s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/images/56.jpeg', 'Dove Hair Love Moisturizing Kids Daily Shampoo with Shea Butter and Coconut Oil, 17.5 fl oz', 'Dove', 6.98, 300, 'Canada', '17.5 fl oz', 'Dove Hair Love Moisturizing Kids Daily Shampoo with Shea Butter and Coconut Oil, kids textured hair deserves expert care, that\'s why Dove Kids Hair Care Moisturizing Shampoo, featuring Zuri from the award-winning animated film \"Hair Love,\" is specially designed for children to enhance the natural beauty of curls, coils, and waves. Our kids shampoo is infused with shea butter and coconut oil to nourish coils, curls, and waves, for soft, moisturized, and healthy-feeling hair. Bringing out the best in your kids hair texture has never been easier. Our moisturizing hair shampoo is made with a fun coconut cookie scent and a gentle formula. Our shampoo and conditioner range is made with shea butter and coconut oil, so your kids can embrace their natural and unique texture and give their hair an extra dose of care with every wash.');
